OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1783711191
OL,3,CPublic urged to avoid Victoria Marine
OL,4,CLake after child pulled through seawall
OL,6,FIslanders have been asked to avoid
OL,7,Fswimming, entering or walking around
OL,8,Fthe Victoria Marine Lake at West Park
OL,9,Fafter a child was pulled through an
OL,10,Fopening in the seawall by the tide.
OL,12,FThe child was safely rescued and
OL,13,Fescaped with minor injuries, where
OL,14,Fthey were treated at the Emergency
OL,15,FDepartment.
OL,17,FThe incident happened on 21 June, but
OL,18,Fwas only reported to the
OL,19,FInfrastructure department on 1 July.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
