OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1783711191
OL,3,CPublic urged to avoid Victoria Marine
OL,4,CLake after child pulled through seawall
OL,6,FThe department says the incident has
OL,7,Fhighlighted the dangers and
OL,8,F"significant safety risks" of the
OL,9,F"deteriorating condition of the
OL,10,Fstructure".
OL,12,FOfficers have introduced immediate
OL,13,Fmeasures to prevent a similar incident
OL,14,Ffrom taking place and are considering
OL,15,Finstalling physical barriers.
OL,17,FThey are also reminding islanders:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
