OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1783711191
OL,3,CPublic urged to avoid Victoria Marine
OL,4,CLake after child pulled through seawall
OL,6,FJersey's Infrastructure Minister,
OL,7,FDeputy Jonathan Renouf, said: "We are
OL,8,Fextremely fortunate that this serious
OL,9,Fincident did not result in a tragedy.
OL,11,F"While the child involved thankfully
OL,12,Fescaped with minor injuries, under
OL,13,Fdifferent circumstances, the outcome
OL,14,Fcould have been far more serious, and
OL,15,Fpotentially fatal.
OL,17,FThe safety of islanders and visitors
OL,18,Fis our first and immediate priority."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
