PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1783711191
OL,3,CPublic urged to avoid Victoria Marine
OL,4,CLake after child pulled through seawall
OL,6,FThe Minister confirmed that the
OL,7,Fdepartment is urgently assessing
OL,8,Ffurther measures to reduce the risk to
OL,9,Fislanders.
OL,11,FEngineers are also assessing those
OL,12,Fimmediate risks and are working on
OL,13,Fplans for longer-term solutions for
OL,14,Fthe pool.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
